Class
Description
Bot
Abstract base class for all bot implementations in the snake game.

Smart bot implementation that uses pathfinding to chase nearest food.

Stupid bot implementation with random movement patterns.
Direction
Represents the four possible movement directions in the game.
Food
 
GameBoard
Represents the game state and manages all game entities.
GameController
Main game controller handling business logic and user input.
GameView
Handles visual representation of game state using JavaFX Canvas.

Provides UI for selecting game level configuration and number of bots.
Main
Main application class for Snake game with bots.

Basic level implementation containing game configuration parameters.

Represents a snake entity with movement and growth logic.
